room_title: Escape room "Legend of Sasquatch" by Escape Hour in Wabash
room_description: A local farmer in Wabash County claims to have seen Bigfoot.  Your curiosity soon gets the best of you. You get a group together and begin your search to find and prove the elusive Sasquatch is real.  You  use an old cabin in the woods as your research base and begin your search for evidence in the woods.  Can you find some hair for DNA testing? Can you find footprints?  Can you get the holy grail, a picture,  and escape the cabin to show your proof?
